casebody.data:
In re Resignation of Harkins.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Harkins (1990), 49 Ohio St. 3d 605.]

(No. 90-168 Submitted February 7, 1990 Decided February 21, 1990.)

The resignation of Clyde Patrick Harkins as an attorney is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
